Sir Elias George Kulukundis OBE (born 1932 in London), known as Sir Eddie Kulukundis, is a member of a Greek shipping family whose professional career has spanned shipping and the theatre.
As a philanthropist he has donated more than Â£2 million to British athletics and theatre groups. Kulukundis was made an OBE for services to British sport in 1993, and knighted for services to British theatre and sport in 1998. He is married to British actress Susan Hampshire.


